<BR> 	At that time, while the same Lentulus and Silvanus were consuls, an angel announced to <A CLASS="help" HREF="../names/e/elizabeth.html#1">Elizabeth</A> about [the birth of] <A CLASS="help" HREF="../names/j/john.html#4">John</A>, on 25th March. 
