<BR> 	In the sixth month, Mary went to her relative Elizabeth.   <A CLASS="ref" NAME="51A">[51A]</A> Elizabeth greeted her and said, "Why am I so favoured, that the mother of my Lord should come to me?  The baby in my womb leaped for joy and blessed you."
